                    </p>
                    <h3>Mersin Uncontested Divorce Lawyer Fee</h3>
                    <p>
                        These types of cases are filed by signing a contract on issues such as compensation, alimony, and representation. Less effort and overtime are spent in uncontested divorce cases. Therefore, the fees of <strong>Mersin divorce lawyers</strong> are lower in uncontested cases. However, the minimum fee for uncontested divorce cases is 4080 TL. In these cases, the <strong>Mersin lawyer fee</strong> is generally between 6000 TL and 15,000 TL.
                    </p>
                    <h3>Mersin Contested Divorce Case Fee</h3>
